DiffieHellmanExchange
public static class DiffieHellmanExchange.RequestData
extends KeyRequestData

Diffie-Hellman key request data.

{ "#mandatory" : [ "parametersid", "publickey" ], "parametersid" : "string", "publickey" : "base64", } where:

  • parametersid identifies the Diffie-Hellman paramters to use
  • publickey the Base64-encoded public key used to generate the shared secret

Constructor Detail

DiffieHellmanExchange.RequestData

public DiffieHellmanExchange.RequestData(String parametersId,
                                         BigInteger publicKey,
                                         DHPrivateKey privateKey)
Create a new Diffie-Hellman request data repository with the specified parameters ID and public key. The private key is also required but is not included in the request data.

Parameters:
parametersId - the parameters ID.
publicKey - the public key Y-value.
privateKey - the private key.

DiffieHellmanExchange.RequestData

public DiffieHellmanExchange.RequestData(JSONObject keyDataJO)
                                  throws MslEncodingException,
                                         MslKeyExchangeException
Create a new Diffie-Hellman request data repository from the provided JSON object. The private key will be unknown.

Parameters:
keyDataJO - the JSON object.
Throws:
MslEncodingException - if there is an error parsing the JSON.
MslKeyExchangeException - if the public key is invalid.
